Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our people emailed us and asked us if we would go on YouTube
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and put up some of the things because there wasn't anything about us up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So we put a couple of little clips up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you'd like to take a look, we're up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, I'll introduce Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have lots of learning to do today, so it'll be fun.
