Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first thing we wanted to do is just, for those that are new, review the, the reason all these lectures started was the discovery of how to tell truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was such a startling discovery that it knocked me out for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I began to write about it, and using an investigative technique, which is ultra-simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very complicated to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We devised a map that goes from 1 to 1,000 of all possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the test for truth is very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The mathematics of why it works depends on advanced quantum mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And the best explanation is in the new book by, what's his name, from Berkeley?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Henry Stapp, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mindful Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:10:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who explains it in much greater detail than I do, that it's based on quantum, the quantum reality, that in infinite space, the infinite field of consciousness, there is no location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere is equally present at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, if I hold a question in my mind, if I hold a statement in my mind, I don't have to be connected with it in time or place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to be connected with it in time or place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to be connected with it in time or place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to be connected with it in time or place or distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I press down Susan's arm, then when I reach a certain level, that will be the level of the truth of what I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, she doesn't know what I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She has no idea what I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it has nothing to do with suggestion or other plausibilities that people have suggested, such as dowsing or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she doesn't know what I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can she respond to what I'm holding in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She does it because I close the gap of what's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I collapse the wave function from possibility to actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If what I'm holding in mind has an actuality, then it has a power, and the power makes her arm go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If what I'm holding in mind is not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,not real, then it has no possibility of existing, and her arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The explanation is intriguing, but it's very, very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll see we do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone is able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher the level of consciousness of the people involved, the more accurate the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So it means that having the capacity to be detached,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to be detached and objective.
