Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know who I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So how would she know that it's a 570?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's one of the greatest teachers of all time, which we'll get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So she has no idea who I was holding in mind.
