Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So the skeptic cuts his own throat because he's getting rid of something of extreme use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So what was mind-boggling about the discovery some decades ago
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:13:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,was that you could tell truth from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and you could do it about anything, anywhere in time or place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the infinite field of consciousness has no dimension,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is everywhere equally present.
