Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.97,0:42:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can imagine the moral conflicts, the moral conflict that every president is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.37,0:42:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So every time I look at a president, what I see is the tremendous moral conflict that he has
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.35,0:42:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in almost every turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.55,0:42:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost every turn has a moral implication, not just a legal, not just a political, but also a moral.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.57,0:42:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you look at the releasing of the atomic bomb at the end of the Second World War and imagine,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.15,0:42:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you look at the releasing of the atomic bomb at the end of the Second World War and imagine,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.39,0:42:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you look at the releasing of the atomic bomb at the end of the Second World War and imagine,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.43,0:42:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to make up your mind about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.55,0:42:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.78,0:43:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So Billy Graham then shows the coherence of reason and the success of putting the two together.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.00,0:43:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremism then comes out of conflict, whereas moderation, moderation comes out of coherence.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.44,0:43:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.43,0:43:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think of the ACLU, I think of the Grinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.81,0:43:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The ACLU is just like the Grinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.47,0:43:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you all see the Grinch again?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.83,0:43:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they showed it quite a bit this last Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.91,0:43:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Grinch just hates Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.05,0:43:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Michael Neundau and Madeline O'Hare in the far left, they just hate Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.79,0:43:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Grinch, I never calibrated the Grinch or the Dickens Christmas Carol.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.83,0:43:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grinch symbolizes an energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.27,0:43:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.43,0:43:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to do the Grinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.85,0:44:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grinch calibrates over 190, 170, 150, 155, 160, 160, 170, around 165.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.06,0:44:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Grinch is around 165.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.07,0:44:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's where the founder of the ACLU came in, the Grinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.62,0:44:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dickens Christmas Carol raises contrast.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.14,0:44:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dickens Christmas Carol, we have permission to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.88,0:44:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 460, 500, 520.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.76,0:44:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 510.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.50,0:44:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dickens Christmas Carol is 510.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.70,0:44:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It exhibits a totally different paradigm, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.26,0:44:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So here we have the Grinch, and the head Grinch right now is Michael Neundau.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.47,0:44:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Madeline turned over her crown to Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.62,0:44:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the tradition of the Grinch is carried on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.32,0:44:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Christmas Carol, of course, is such a wonderful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.03,0:45:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Conflict in today's world is certainly centered around the Koran.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.29,0:45:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,One reason it's centered around the Koran is that about 30% of the verses of the Koran calibrate below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.17,0:45:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, 15% calibrate below 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.25,0:45:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate below 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.99,0:45:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.47,0:45:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Koran does not even agree with itself, if you've ever read the Koran.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.69,0:45:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people have read the Koran here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.82,0:45:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite a bit of work to read from beginning to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.70,0:45:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's sort of patched together from all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.44,0:45:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But the difficulty with the Koran, you see, because we're talking about conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.30,0:45:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and we can see the Koran is central to today's international conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.30,0:45:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the verses do not agree with themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.60,0:45:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They do not agree with themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.78,0:46:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And so there's endless conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.12,0:46:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say anything you want, and then justified by the fact that it's in the Koran.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.54,0:46:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can kill all the infidels, and it's there in the Koran.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.42,0:46:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll tell you, kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.70,0:46:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you get some kind of coherence out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.84,0:46:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the principle of abrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.38,0:46:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't read the Koran without understanding the principle of abrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.12,0:46:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What it means is,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.79,0:46:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is towards the back of the Koran overrules that which is in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.19,0:46:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So if in an early chapter it says,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.99,0:46:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,allow something, and then in the later chapter it says,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.03,0:46:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,do not allow something,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.87,0:46:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,then what you come away with is you do not allow.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.71,0:46:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So abrogation is an attempt to synthesize
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.90,0:46:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is intrinsically within itself in conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.84,0:46:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The abrogation...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.60,0:47:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you cannot read the Koran without being aware
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.32,0:47:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that the later chapters cancel out the early one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.68,0:47:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the biggest impacts in today's world is addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.26,0:47:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's certainly currently in the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.40,0:47:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All the stars, everybody dying from one addiction or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.86,0:47:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All the famous people, the Hollywood stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.85,0:47:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So addiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.25,0:47:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then is, of course, very conflictual.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.05,0:47:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very poorly understood by the public at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.03,0:47:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even well understood by some of the professionals
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.71,0:47:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that come on and talk learnedly about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.63,0:47:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly shows conflict within the person
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.66,0:47:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as between the person and their relationships and the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.16,0:48:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And the synthesis, the synthesis that allows the resolution of the conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.34,0:48:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of course, is the 12th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.50,0:48:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the 12th-step groups have had a major impact on our culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.88,0:48:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Quietly, they have the most positive impact of any...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.87,0:48:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In the book I just finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.67,0:48:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we did the impact of the various religions it saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.55,0:48:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So Christianity, Judaism, and all those formal traditional religions,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.92,0:48:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,their impact on society calibrates at 450.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.46,0:48:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That certainly is a high degree of goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.40,0:48:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That shows a high degree of coherence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.08,0:48:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Of reason and faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.58,0:48:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The 12-step groups, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.18,0:48:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,impact U.S. society at level 570.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.28,0:48:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's far beyond the 450.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.76,0:48:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So the impact that 12-step groups have on society
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.22,0:48:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is of a higher level and more profound than even classic religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.17,0:49:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And most people seek out 12-step groups now for a great variety.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.29,0:49:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only alcoholism, but all kinds of addictions and misbehaviors
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.07,0:49:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and psychological difficulties.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.02,0:49:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the 12-step groups synthesize into coherence,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.86,0:49:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,synthesize reason and logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.28,0:49:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It synthesizes content in terms of context.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.55,0:49:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And the 12 steps of AA are really good for everybody to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.24,0:49:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because whatever problem you have in life,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.62,0:49:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,if you apply the 12 steps to it, you'll resolve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.16,0:49:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.44,0:49:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an amazing statement, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.76,0:49:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.82,0:49:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even if you're broke,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.34,0:49:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or just, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.34,0:50:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.56,0:50:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.19,0:50:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So everybody in our society knows
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.72,0:50:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that 12-step groups are benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.90,0:50:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Benign in intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.66,0:50:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're totally non-conflictual.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.12,0:50:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They have no opinion on outside issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.48,0:50:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't get into an argument with them
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.34,0:50:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because they don't have any position you can argue with.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.48,0:50:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So they exhibit probably the highest value
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.20,0:50:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of a social group in our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.08,0:50:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And they've infiltrated all levels of government
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.58,0:50:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.50,0:50:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,government.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.14,0:50:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Various people who are extremely well-known
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.12,0:50:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,have recovered in the 12-step groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.68,0:50:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So they form a paradigm of recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.78,0:50:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from almost anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.64,0:50:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gambling, sexual addiction, being a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.48,0:51:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are addicted to being a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.62,0:51:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you get so much juice out of being a failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.76,0:51:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you just can't help but keep feeling it over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.44,0:51:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see a negative pattern in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.68,0:51:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest looking into the 12-step groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.24,0:51:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And learning the 12 steps and applying it to that problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.99,0:51:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're stupid and ugly,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.99,0:51:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you can end up happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.66,0:51:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just let go on to change it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.78,0:51:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and turn it over to God and pray for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.56,0:51:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.02,0:51:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you may be ugly, but you're lovable.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.12,0:51:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.06,0:51:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be stupid and ugly, but you're huggable.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.72,0:51:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.36,0:51:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What more do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.10,0:51:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What more do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.72,0:51:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.90,0:51:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So any questions about that right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.04,0:51:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody got any burning question about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.32,0:51:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How these things calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.64,0:51:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and the contrast between reason and faith?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.48,0:51:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can see they can be used to support each other
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.22,0:51:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,or to attack each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.56,0:52:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is conflictual then uses it to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.02,0:52:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So these extremes here bring about disruption in society.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.60,0:52:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And what we see,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.92,0:52:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what we strive for in our own spiritual life
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.14,0:52:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is a synthesis of reason and faith
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.60,0:52:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,into a workable daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.10,0:52:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next one now?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.55,0:52:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.38,0:52:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's slide two, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.90,0:52:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.69,0:52:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.53,0:52:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.30,0:52:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so conflict then comes out of,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.56,0:52:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we've said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.48,0:52:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,left brain and right brain have different functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.74,0:52:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And this audience is relatively familiar with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.66,0:52:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The left brain has to do with reason and logic
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.07,0:52:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the right brain has to do with synthesis
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.56,0:52:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and love and coherence.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.58,0:53:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's considerable difficulty in people
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.98,0:53:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,from these two different populations.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.66,0:53:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The left brain people have a great deal of difficulty
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.58,0:53:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding right brain people and vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.04,0:53:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The left brain people are in considerable conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.36,0:53:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And so people will say,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.94,0:53:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,how are we gonna bring about accommodation
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.07,0:53:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with that which is inimicable?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.33,0:53:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And actually, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.07,0:53:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I listen to all the accommodation people.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.33,0:53:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, yeah, right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.24,0:53:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And shoot you dead the minute you walk out the door
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.62,0:53:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,from the accommodation conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.12,0:53:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the difficulty is left brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.32,0:53:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,right brain synthesize and see things
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.82,0:53:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and process things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.34,0:53:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't bring that slide today.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.86,0:54:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have the slide, but everybody's familiar with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.68,0:54:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That the right brain releases endorphins,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.52,0:54:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,different neurotransmitters than the left brain does.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.04,0:54:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So these people live in two different societies.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.76,0:54:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They actually live in two different societies,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.62,0:54:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,although the population is co-mingled.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.94,0:54:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The left brainers live in a different society
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.19,0:54:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,than the right brainers resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.34,0:54:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They live in a different society.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.38,0:54:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's one way to help overcome conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.28,0:54:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is to see that people process things differently
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.50,0:54:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and make allowance for the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.36,0:54:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that that's the way they process things.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.23,0:54:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That allows them to be wrong without you being mad at them.
