Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.21,1:08:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So the technique that we follow is the only way I know of
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.21,1:08:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to avoid placing faith in falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.21,1:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And faith in falsehood, of course, is endemic.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.40,1:09:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the book that made it, it was popular,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.50,1:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Extraordinary Popular Delusions in the Madness of Crowds.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.50,1:09:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I refer to that very often because it's appropriate for today's world.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.50,1:09:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can turn on the television anytime
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.50,1:09:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will see an extraordinary popular delusion
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.50,1:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,dominating society right this minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.50,1:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on which gets the most money.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.50,1:09:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the popular delusion is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.16,1:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Extraordinary Popular Delusions in the Madness of Crowds.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.16,1:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's offset by the verifying the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.16,1:09:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and by the balance of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.16,1:09:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You notice how causes become very popular.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.55,1:09:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The narcissistic core of the ego loves causes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.55,1:09:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to save this, we're going to save that,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.55,1:09:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to save the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.55,1:09:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And the amount of advertising is staggering.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.77,1:10:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.35,1:10:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And we find out things all the time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.35,1:10:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say I'm going to take something that sounds real great.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.99,1:10:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.99,1:10:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hold this program in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.99,1:10:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That program calibrates over 200, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.99,1:10:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nets. We're going to solve malaria with nets.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.75,1:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's take the next one.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.75,1:10:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take the next one.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.09,1:10:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind calibrates over 200, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.09,1:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to save the Himalayan, people of the Himalayans.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.31,1:10:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose is spent on those two big ads?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.56,1:10:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They come on every freaking night over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.56,1:10:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds logical.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.37,1:10:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten dollars for a net.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.72,1:10:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Save lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.72,1:11:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How come it calibrates below 200?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.75,1:11:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.55,1:11:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the poor people in the Himalayas?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.55,1:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving money to them, isn't that going to help?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.85,1:11:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it under 200 if it's so true?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.84,1:11:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it under 200?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.16,1:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.24,1:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Save lives with nets.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.24,1:11:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of those deals, you send ten dollars for a net,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.23,1:11:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say, well, you could pay a whole year in advance, send us 120,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.23,1:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I did that once with one of those things, save the children deals.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.23,1:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way it went, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.23,1:11:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You got worked up for the money, and I don't know where the money went
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.23,1:11:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're still after the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.01,1:11:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you've got the difference between appearance and illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.01,1:11:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They take the Dalai Lama's picture out of someplace
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.59,1:11:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and they tack it onto the end of the ad,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.59,1:11:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's begging you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.59,1:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's begging you to please save the people in the Himalayas.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.13,1:12:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it calibrate under 200?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.13,1:12:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates under 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.79,1:12:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.01,1:12:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dalai Lama doesn't calibrate under 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.01,1:12:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's 570.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.27,1:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody took his picture and put it on this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.27,1:12:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, you want to know how to tell truth from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.27,1:12:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you become a little more perceptive.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.27,1:12:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You get much sharper at picking up that you're being had all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.40,1:12:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a lot of the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.64,1:12:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.24,1:12:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always being had.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.24,1:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.65,1:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They put a product up, they put a star.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.65,1:12:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In your mind, that product is a star, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.65,1:12:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already been programmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.48,1:12:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're programmed, programmed, programmed, programmed, programmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.48,1:12:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So your mind, which you think is so wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.48,1:12:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is one set of endless stupid programmings.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.50,1:13:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worthless.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.76,1:13:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's handy for counting your change.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.76,1:13:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about all it's good for.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.64,1:13:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you begin to look elsewhere for truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.64,1:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to look elsewhere for truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.67,1:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And orders from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.89,1:13:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.76,1:13:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a break so you can get over the shock
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.76,1:13:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of what I just got through telling you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.52,1:13:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to cure the world of malaria.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.32,1:13:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll take a short break.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.32,1:13:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.32,1:13:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
